data.description: This home has a large eat in kitchen and formal dining room with wood floors throughout.20x20 Loft area above garage with stairs inside and out for easy access.Enjoy the large beautifully landscaped yard from your 20x20 deck with cable hook-up for entertaining.Conveniently located just 30 minutes to Canton and Alliance.This home qualifies for the USDA loan 100% financing for qualified buyers.
